<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The following shall be excluded from any repayment by guarantee schemes: </inglise>
<eesti> Tagatisskeemid ei h&uuml;vita j&auml;rgmist: </eesti>
<inglise> - subject to Article 8 (3), deposits made by other credit institutions on their own behalf and for their own account, </inglise>
